node.text: Cleaning out some old stuff as I prepare for one last semester before moving to Nashville full time and I stumbled upon my old hockey cards. It brought back so much nostalgia looking through all of them again. Even had my man @cmace30 on the front page! 😂 Just being honest, I probably won’t be on here much the next few months. Not like I’ve been super active lately anyway lol. Gotta study and take the CPA exam before graduation in May so I’ll catch y’all on the other side!✌️
